title: CAN FNATIC STILL MAKE IT OUT OF GROUPS??????

replies.body: They've got a couple days to practice and fix the problems that are happening. They can easily make it out of Groups, I'm not really sure they'll get first in group though. I think because how the table works if cloud 9 wins one more they won't get first.
I HAVE FAITH..........THAT C9 WILL GO 0-3!!!!!!!(like a certain other Chinese team from week one)

I say that anyone in any of the tables can come on top, taking into account their dedication and passion!
I say fnatic can do it :D

GO ****** FNATIC
